backend.queue
Class ProgramQueue

java.lang.Object
  backend.queue.ProgramQueue

public class ProgramQueue
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains all the StationQueues that are associated with this ProgramQueue. A StationQueue should exist for every station that exists in a program, unless the file heirarchy has been changed since the last login.

Author:
Kayre Hylton
